<DOCNO> LA120594-0090 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 105114 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
December 5, 1994, Monday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part C; Page 14; Column 1; Sports Desk 
</P>
