 As Richard Simon recited the prayer for lighting the Hanukkah candles -- 
"Baruch Atah Adonai . . . " -- his 4-year-old son, Andrew, interrupted: 
</P>
<P>
 "No, Daddy, not in Spanish."  
</P>
