 Roberto Martinez of the American Friends Service Committee in San Diego said 
he thinks an effective campaign discouraging tourists and conventions can be 
launched by early next year. 
</P>
<P>
 "Rather than demoralize us, the passage of 187 has reinforced our commitment 
to organize, mobilize and educate all people of goodwill in the defense of 
human rights," said Maria Jimenez of the American Friends Service Committee in 
